<h2 id="lists-of-and-information-about-organisations-the-department-is-responsible-for-those-it-works-in-partnership-with-and-those-it-sponsors">Lists of and information about organisations the department is responsible for, those it works in partnership with and those it sponsors</h2>

<p>The Attorney General superintends the <a rel="external" href="http://www.cps.gov.uk">Crown Prosecution Service</a> and the <a rel="external" href="http://www.sfo.gov.uk/">Serious Fraud Office</a></p>

<p>He also appoints HM Chief Inspector of the <a rel="external" href="http://www.hmcpsi.gov.uk/">Crown Prosecution Service</a> and is the minister responsible for the work of the <a rel="external" href="http://www.justiceinspectorates.gov.uk/hmcpsi/">Government Legal Department</a></p>

